程序包 beans

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Food
    Represents one of the types of menuitem, the ala carte item
    MenuItem
    Represents general menuitem
    Order
    Represents the order that customer gives, will be created in two cases: when customer directly walks in or when customer check in to a reservation
    Reservation
    Represents the reservation the customer books
    SetPackage
    Represents one of the types of menuitem, the set package item
    Staff
    Represents the staff in the restaurant
    Table
    Represents the table in the restaurant
